title: fanoutqa: What are the birthdates of the chancellors or presidents of the top 5 US public universities by endowment size? (7af8d2c46234eac4)

chat_history.content: What are the birthdates of the chancellors or presidents of the top 5 US public universities by endowment size?

Here are the dates of birth of the presidents or chancellors of the top 5 US public universities by endowment size, as of 2022:

1. University of Texas System: James B. Milliken (Chancellor) - August 14, 1957.
2. University of California: Michael V. Drake (President) - March 9, 1951.
3. University of Michigan: Mark S. Schlissel (President) - April 25, 1957.
4. University of Virginia: James E. Ryan (President) - Birthdate not found.
5. University of North Carolina: Joseph  N.  Mangano (Interim President) - Birthdate not found.

Note: The University of Virginia's James E. Ryan and the University of North Carolina's Joseph N. Mangano's birthdates were not found during the search.
